import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import cv2
from Image import Show
from ImageSignal import ImageSignal,pyzbar

$\textbf{A :}\text{ find Layers:}$

In [2]:
img1 = cv2.imread('images/qr2.png')
s1= ImageSignal.segment_watershed(img1,inv=True,size=1)

img2 = cv2.imread('images/tq.jpg')
s2= ImageSignal.segment_watershed(img2,inv=True,size=1)

img3 = cv2.imread('images/t2.jpg')
s3= ImageSignal.segment_watershed(img3,inv=True,size=2,num=True)

img4 = cv2.imread('images/t3.png')
s4= ImageSignal.segment_watershed(img4,inv=False,size=3)

img5 = cv2.imread('images/t4.jpg')
s5= ImageSignal.segment_watershed(img5,inv=False,size=2,num=False)

img6 = cv2.imread('images/qr4.png')
s6= ImageSignal.segment_watershed(img6,inv=True,size=2,num=False)



Show.compareim(cv2.cvtColor(s1,cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB),cv2.cvtColor(s2,cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB),size=1.2)
Show.compareim(cv2.cvtColor(s3,cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB),cv2.cvtColor(s4,cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB),size=1.2)
Show.compareim(cv2.cvtColor(s5,cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB),cv2.cvtColor(s6,cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB),size=1.2)

$\textbf{B :}\text{ find pixel and seperate Layers:}$

In [3]:
img2 = cv2.imread('images/tq.jpg')
img3 = cv2.imread('images/t2.jpg')
img4 = cv2.imread('images/t3.png')

warped2,pixel2=[],[]
warped3,pixel3=[],[]
warped4,pixel4=[],[]

pts2,image2= ImageSignal.QR_point(img2.copy(),inv=True,ratio=40,num=True)
pts3,image3= ImageSignal.QR_point(img3.copy(),inv=True,ratio=40,num=True)
pts4,image4= ImageSignal.QR_point(img4.copy(),inv=False,ratio=16,num=True)



for row in pts2:
    [warp,width,height]=ImageSignal.four_point_transform(image2,row)
    warped2.append(warp)
    pixel2.append(str(width)+'*'+str(height))
for row in pts3:
    [warp,width,height]=ImageSignal.four_point_transform(image3,row)
    warped3.append(warp)
    pixel3.append(str(width)+'*'+str(height))
for row in pts4:
    [warp,width,height]=ImageSignal.four_point_transform(image4,row)
    warped4.append(warp)
    pixel4.append(str(width)+'*'+str(height))


Show.show_segments(warped2,pixel2,Qr=0)
Show.compareim(cv2.cvtColor(img2,cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB),cv2.cvtColor(s2,cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB),size=1.2);plt.show()
Show.show_segments(warped3,pixel3,Qr=0)
Show.compareim(cv2.cvtColor(img3,cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB),cv2.cvtColor(s3,cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB),size=1.2);plt.show()
Show.show_segments(warped4,pixel4,Qr=0)
Show.compareim(cv2.cvtColor(img4,cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB),cv2.cvtColor(s4,cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB),size=1.2);plt.show()
